that I told my father about it.

25
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:29,120
Isn't that a good thing?

26
00:03:29,760 --> 00:03:30,800
Why are you being punished?

27
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,200
My father said

28
00:03:34,640 --> 00:03:35,760
when the moon is full,
it begins to wane.

29
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,320
Doing well is expected

30
00:03:39,640 --> 00:03:40,920
but being happy about it isn't.

31
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,320
Good is good.

32
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:47,320
Happy is Happy.

33
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:48,320
Don't listen to his nonsense.

34
00:03:48,640 --> 00:03:50,920
Shh, don't speak ill of my father.

35
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:52,280
He was wrong.

36
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,400
He shouldn't have criticized you.

37
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:59,280
You're really rude!

38
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,600
This is

39
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:06,520
what they call a general's boldness.

40
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:09,320
Climbing over someone's wall
in the middle of the night.

41
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:11,320
Is that what a general does?

42
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,760
Don't look down on me.

43
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:15,320
I'm the Champion Marquis
conferred by His Majesty

44
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:17,240
and the youngest general of Great Yu.

45
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:23,920
My...

46
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:26,320
My name is Xie Tinghan.

47
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:27,520
What's yours?

48
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:32,960
I...

49
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:36,080
I'm the legitimate daughter
of the Jiang family,

50
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:38,880
Jiang Mingyue.

51
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:55,840
They were right indeed.

52
00:04:58,640 --> 00:04:59,680
What did you say?

53
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,280
The bright moon of the Jiang family

54
