55
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,320
Greetings, Your Majesty.

56
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:47,320
Why does my beloved consort seem so sad

57
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:52,040
on such a beautiful night?

58
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:54,720
When a beauty weeps,

59
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:57,840
it pains my heart.

60
00:05:59,160 --> 00:05:59,880
Your Majesty,

61
00:06:00,760 --> 00:06:01,640
I'm just...

62
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:04,320
I'm just missing my family.

63
00:06:09,960 --> 00:06:12,160
Just missing your family?

64
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:13,480
Your Majesty,

65
00:06:14,440 --> 00:06:14,960
I...

66
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:16,920
I have no other intentions.

67
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,160
It's best that way.

68
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,160
Your Majesty,

69
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:43,800
I...

70
00:06:44,280 --> 00:06:45,400
I'm pregnant.

71
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,360
That's fine.

72
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:52,160
