You don't know me?

79
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:44,840
I'm here to see Miss Jiang.

80
00:07:44,880 --> 00:07:46,480
Miss Jiang isn't home.

81
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,920
Miss Xie, no need to come by anymore.

82
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,720
Wait a minute.

83
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:50,240
No need to come by?

84
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,120
What do you mean?

85
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:53,040
Where is Yue?

86
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:55,080
Well...

87
00:07:57,640 --> 00:07:59,240
Eunuch Wei, you came.

88
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:01,600
Ask Minister Jiang
to receive the decree.

89
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:03,080
Your family's very lucky.

90
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:04,720
Miss Jiang is pregnant
with the imperial heir

91
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:07,160
and has been conferred the title
of Consort Li by His Majesty.

92
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,400
Please come in, Eunuch Wei.

93
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:10,960
Wait a minute!

94
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:13,720
Consort Li? Imperial heir?

95
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:15,520
Is that Yue?

96
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,720
What's going on?

97
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:18,360
Exactly what you heard.

98
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:19,280
You should leave now.

99
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:22,360
Wait!

100
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:24,160
Open the door!

101
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,320
I must send word to my brother.

102
00:08:33,460 --> 00:08:36,890
♪The autumn wind stirs a ripple♪

103
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:41,000
♪Before the blossoms
could scent the earth♪

104
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:47,320
[Marriage Proposal]

105
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:50,760
[Xie Tinghan and Jiang Mingyue
are to be wed in a harmonious union.]

106
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:52,870
[We present a dowry of gold, jewels,
silk and dresses for you.]

107
00:08:52,870 --> 00:08:56,030
♪Sighing for the fate of all beings♪

108
00:08:56,400 --> 00:09:01,100
♪Unable to seek the bond we once shared♪

109
00:09:01,590 --> 00:09:03,550
♪How deep was the love♪

110
00:09:03,850 --> 00:09:05,810
♪Leaving me with scars♪

111
00:09:06,050 --> 00:09:09,520
♪Love and hate became fleeting years,
turning us into old acquaintances♪

112
00:09:09,780 --> 00:09:11,700
♪The candlelight disturbs♪

113
00:09:11,940 --> 00:09:15,750
♪Whispers by the western window
seem to lock a deep night♪

114
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:19,520
Stop!

115
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:22,120
Sir,

116
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:24,160
