throwing lucky coins.

117
00:09:24,160 --> 00:09:25,480
We'll have to wait a while.

118
00:09:26,400 --> 00:09:27,080
It's fine.

119
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:30,230
♪Leaving traces of sorrow♪

120
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:41,760
Sir Xie, these are lucky coins
from His Majesty.

121
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:42,600
Take a few coins

122
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,480
for the good luck.

123
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:44,680
May you

124
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:46,840
and your beloved have a child soon

125
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:48,640
and grow old together.

126
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:49,640
Thank you.

127
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:53,280
Why did His Majesty suddenly
confer consorts?

128
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:57,400
His Majesty summoned over ten maidens
to the palace recently.

129
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:59,680
Only Consort Li is pregnant
with the imperial heir.

130
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:00,720
She's truly fortunate.

131
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:04,520
I heard she's the daughter of
a high-ranking official named Jiang.

132
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:06,640
♪Leaving me with scars♪

133
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:08,760
What did you say?

134
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,120
Sir Xie,

135
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:10,960
what's wrong?

136
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,530
♪The candlelight disturbs♪

137
00:10:12,680 --> 00:10:13,720
Are you sure?

138
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:16,600
Whose daughter is Consort Li?

139
00:10:18,040 --> 00:10:21,520
She's the daughter of Minister Jiang,
Commander of the Imperial Guards.

140
00:10:21,590 --> 00:10:25,050
♪Why does spring rush by?
The silent rain drenches a pair♪

141
00:10:26,560 --> 00:10:28,000
Sir Xie!

142
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:28,800
What's wrong?

143
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:30,560
Sir Xie!

144
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:37,280
♪When the dream ends,
we finally become old acquaintances♪

145
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:37,960
Yue...

146
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:38,680
Yue!

147
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:16,680
Tinghan!

148
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:18,760
Tinghan!

149
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,120
Yin,

150
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,400
have you seen Yue?

151
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:23,760
She...

152
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:24,920
She's still at the Jiang Mansion,

153
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:25,720
isn't she?

154
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,400
Isn't she?

155
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:30,160
Calm down.

156
00:11:30,800 --> 00:11:31,320
Sit down.

157
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:32,200
Sit.

158
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:38,400
Tinghan,

159
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,080
calm yourself.

160
00:11:41,800 --> 00:11:42,640
Yue...

161
00:11:44,880 --> 00:11:45,800
She's entered the palace.

162
00:11:48,880 --> 00:11:49,800
It's all my fault.

163
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:52,520
I failed to protect Yue.

164
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:54,640
It's no use talking about this now.

165
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,280
What's done is done.

166
00:11:57,560 --> 00:11:59,040
We need to find a solution.

167
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:07,760
Tinghan!

168
00:12:09,800 --> 00:12:10,880
What are you going to do?

169
00:12:12,400 --> 00:12:14,040
Yue won't like the palace.

170
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:16,400
I must get her out.

171
00:12:16,560 --> 00:12:17,440
As a third-rank border general,

172
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:19,800
you'll enter the palace armed

173
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:20,920
and abduct a consort?

174
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:23,440
Have you thought about the consequences?

175
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:27,520
Tinghan.

176
00:12:28,560 --> 00:12:29,360
Tinghan,

177
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:32,600
if you rush into the palace like this,

178
00:12:32,800 --> 00:12:33,920
you could endanger Yue.

179
00:12:42,040 --> 00:12:42,960
Do you mind

180
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:43,880
if she had been married

181
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:45,200
and bore another man's child?

182
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:48,040
If she were happy,

183
00:12:48,760 --> 00:12:50,120
I'd bless her.

184
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:52,080
But she's being forced.

185
00:12:53,160 --> 00:12:54,760
The thought of the suffering
she's enduring

186
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,600
tears my heart apart.

187
00:12:56,680 --> 00:12:57,680
I want to

188
00:12:57,680 --> 00:12:58,720
storm that palace

189
00:12:58,720 --> 00:12:59,880
and kill them all.

190
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:01,000
Then are you willing

191
00:13:01,400 --> 00:13:02,680
to risk your life for her?

192
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:05,280
If it means her freedom,

193
00:13:05,920 --> 00:13:07,200
I fear no death.

194
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:08,280
Good.

195
00:13:09,880 --> 00:13:11,480
There are spies in the Jade Pavilion
within the palace.

196
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,360
Rescuing her won't be difficult.

197
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:15,760
We just need to wait
for the right moment.

198
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:16,800
When the time comes,

199
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:18,720
I'll swap her out

200
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:21,520
and give her a new face.

201
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:23,520
You two can then

202
00:13:24,360 --> 00:13:25,520
live far away at the border

203
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:27,480
and never return to Andu.

204
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:30,560
What if something goes wrong?

205
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:32,320
If I flee,

206
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:34,120
what...

207
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:36,160
what will happen to the Xie family?

208
00:13:36,160 --> 00:13:36,960
As long as I'm here,

209
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:39,640
no one will dare touch the Xie family.

210
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:44,720
Don't worry, Tinghan.

211
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:46,280
I'll find a way to enter the palace

212
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:47,680
and explain everything to Yue.

213
00:13:49,800 --> 00:13:50,600
Good.

214
00:14:04,040 --> 00:14:05,240
I'll wait outside the door.

215
00:14:28,160 --> 00:14:28,960
Yue.

216
00:14:32,160 --> 00:14:32,920
Here,

217
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:35,760
everyone calls me Consort Li.

218
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:39,240
There's no more Mingyue.

219
00:14:39,840 --> 00:14:40,560
Yue,

220
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:42,280
my brother has returned.

221
00:14:42,520 --> 00:14:43,720
We're going to take you out.

222
00:14:45,520 --> 00:14:46,160
Tinghan...

223
00:14:46,520 --> 00:14:47,760
Tinghan has returned to Andu?

224
00:14:48,800 --> 00:14:49,880
Is he hurt?

225
00:14:51,800 --> 00:14:52,680
He's fine.

226
00:14:57,320 --> 00:14:58,480
He's just very worried about you.

227
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:07,800
As long as he's fine...

228
00:15:08,720 --> 00:15:09,840
As long as he's fine.

229
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:12,200
Yue, we've thought of a plan.

230
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:19,800
No, it's too risky.

231
00:15:19,800 --> 00:15:21,040
We must try even if it's risky.

232
00:15:21,760 --> 00:15:23,280
How can we just stand by

233
00:15:23,400 --> 00:15:24,760
and watch you waste away in this palace?

234
00:15:26,920 --> 00:15:28,320
What difference does it make?

235
00:15:29,360 --> 00:15:30,600
My whole life has been

236
00:15:31,640 --> 00:15:35,880
moving from one walled place to another.

237
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:39,400
I'm used to it by now.

238
00:15:41,080 --> 00:15:43,440
Then get used to a new life.

239
00:15:43,640 --> 00:15:45,440
Yue, I promise you,

240
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:46,040
it'll be safe,

241
00:15:46,040 --> 00:15:47,120
completely safe.

242
00:15:47,440 --> 00:15:48,880
As long as you can escape Andu,

243
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:49,880
you and my brother...

244
00:15:49,880 --> 00:15:50,560
Yin,

245
00:15:52,920 --> 00:15:54,120
there's no future

246
00:15:56,040 --> 00:15:57,200
for me and Tinghan anymore.

247
00:16:05,920 --> 00:16:08,080
Is it because you're carrying
the Emperor's child?

248
00:16:08,720 --> 00:16:09,680
You were forced.

249
00:16:09,680 --> 00:16:10,640
We all know that.

250
00:16:10,640 --> 00:16:11,560
My brother said

251
00:16:11,560 --> 00:16:12,160
he doesn't care.

252
00:16:12,160 --> 00:16:13,080
I do.

253
00:16:15,920 --> 00:16:16,720
Yue,

254
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:19,840
we all want you to be safe.

255
00:16:22,760 --> 00:16:23,680
Yin,

256
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:26,760
don't you understand?

257
00:16:28,360 --> 00:16:30,520
The only way I can be safe

258
00:16:31,440 --> 00:16:32,800
is if I fulfill my role as Consort Li

259
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:34,120
and bear the Emperor's heir.

260
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:34,840
Absurd!

261
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:36,890
♪The wind blows cool in autumn again♪

262
00:16:38,840 --> 00:16:40,080
You're leaving today

263
00:16:40,640 --> 00:16:41,600
whether you want to or not!

264
00:16:43,340 --> 00:16:45,280
♪Peach blossoms hidden in dust♪

265
00:17:03,890 --> 00:17:06,080
♪The wind under the eaves♪

266
00:17:06,550 --> 00:17:09,190
♪Gently taps on the wooden door♪

267
00:17:10,940 --> 00:17:13,420
♪The candle flame flickers
as I sleep soundly♪

268
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:16,100
♪The night is at its peak♪

269
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:20,210
♪A thunderclap rolls♪

270
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:23,140
♪Stirring up old dreams again♪

271
00:17:25,280 --> 00:17:27,640
♪Thoughts linger on the warmth
of the past♪

272
00:17:27,830 --> 00:17:31,070
♪The sincerity of the past♪

273
00:17:31,260 --> 00:17:34,420
♪Fireworks fall like rain♪

274
00:17:34,690 --> 00:17:37,690
♪But soon they cool♪

275
00:17:38,240 --> 00:17:41,930
♪I watch as you pass by♪

276
00:17:41,950 --> 00:17:45,040
♪Not daring to ask♪

277
00:17:45,570 --> 00:17:48,860
♪Like the moon, waxing and waning♪

278
00:17:48,860 --> 00:17:51,930
♪How could it ask more?♪

279
00:17:52,200 --> 00:17:57,120
♪You and I are like a small boat
on the river♪

280
00:17:57,380 --> 00:18:02,130
♪Rising and falling with the waves♪

281
00:18:25,040 --> 00:18:27,580
♪Speaking of love and hate♪

282
00:18:27,920 --> 00:18:30,410
♪How can I distinguish them?♪

283
00:18:32,310 --> 00:18:34,700
♪Longing for fate, praying sincerely♪

284
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:38,050
♪Yet the world does not acknowledge it♪

285
00:18:39,110 --> 00:18:41,470
♪The night grows deep♪

286
00:18:41,880 --> 00:18:44,710
♪Old dreams are stirred again♪

287
00:18:46,480 --> 00:18:48,920
♪Yet the old people
are still within them♪

288
00:18:49,110 --> 00:18:52,180
♪Why do they remain silent?♪

289
00:18:52,500 --> 00:18:55,600
♪Fireworks fall like rain♪

290
00:18:55,980 --> 00:18:59,010
♪But soon they cool♪

291
00:18:59,480 --> 00:19:03,190
♪I look, adding a few more strokes
to the word "love"♪

292
00:19:03,360 --> 00:19:06,330
♪A new year's ring♪

293
00:19:06,650 --> 00:19:09,960
♪The cicada's cry is close
and autumn leaves are near♪

294
00:19:10,180 --> 00:19:13,130
♪Yet it's hard to recognize each other♪

295
00:19:13,750 --> 00:19:18,340
♪I sigh, why are you and I♪

296
00:19:18,910 --> 00:19:23,450
♪Rising and falling,
drifting in this way?♪
